 </ul>  
 <p> RRR is a 2022 Indian Telugu-language epic action drama film directed by S. S. Rajamouli,
 who co-wrote the film with V. Vijayendra Prasad.It centers around fictional versions of two Indian 
 revolutionaries, Alluri Sitarama Raju (Charan) and Komaram Bheem (Rama Rao), their friendship, and 
 their fight against the British Raj. RRR received universal praise for Rajamouli's direction, 
 performances, soundtrack, action sequences, and visuals. The film was considered one of the ten best
 films of the year by the National Board of Review, making it only the second non-English language film
 ever to make it to the list. The song "Naatu Naatu" won the Best Original Song award at the 95th Academy 
 Awards, making it the first song from an Indian film, as well as the first from an Asian film, to win in 
 this category.</p>
